{"tid":629853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騙徒入侵WhatsApp　點自保先係最精？","createTime":"2018-04-15T05:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T06:49:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d89448154391497bf4812641bfc605e2f0f269b8","tid":629853,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180415/20361912?_ga=2.15916086.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361912%3F_ga%3D2.15916086.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=wjLnzjBMS3ebGeoGKzojcCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=736e35ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361912%3F_ga%3D2.15916086.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=f35f89a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180415/20361912?_ga=2.15916086.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】騙徒入侵WhatsApp　點自保先係最精？<br />\n<br />\n1.7K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年首季涉及盜用即時通訊應用程式騙案達270宗，較去年同期急升逾9倍，受害人損失金額達260萬元，當中九成案件涉及騙徒透過WhatsApp，利用受害人對親友的信任，欺騙受害人購買「MyCard」點數卡。其中一名中年婦人一日內被騙徒要求購買逾50次點數卡，被騙金額近12萬元。警方倡巿民在WhatsApp啟用「雙步驟驗證」確保安全。"},{"pid":"c7b1aa780ea1272e689e6f7598d31db503a1d6e8","tid":629853,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"uninstall whatsapp"},{"pid":"bf25142ea1f5263f23549608cda2e43f2f9139e0","tid":629853,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T06:49:29.000Z","msg":"轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}